Parameters:

Iterations: 20

LR: 0.008

Num octaves: 3

Octave scale: 1.0

Layers & weights:
{'inception3a': 0.1, 'inception4a': 0.2, 'inception4d': 0.3, 'inception4e': 0.4}

Jitter: 16

Observations:

Original image largely preserved in color and shape

Hallucinations subtle, less hypnotic, eyes appear sparsely

Patterns blend softly with original image

Loss curve shows slow, stable fluctuation

